die brandmauer : der achte fall von kommissar kurt wallander brannvegg very different from sidetracked . there , the first 100 pages were filled with wallender 's repeated introspections , so that the book only took off after that . have read firewall in norwegian translation , partly while we visited s. sweden . the of occurence so many murders so fast in ystad in the book contrasted sharply with the nice reality of street life and cafe atmosphere in ystad in july ! the altstadt is surprisingly large and pretty , not so many gammle byene left in scandinavia .